    "description": "世界上第一手专业无人机飞行员的体验！<br><br>DCL发布一款激发肾上腺素的高速度的免费飞行冒险游戏。玩家在游玩时有两种飞行模式可供选择，指导新手玩家的新手飞行员模式和专业无人机飞行员模式。<br><br>你有其他需要吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/069ad9702fd238c2762726c3ecd75aa3.poster.avif?t=1725013500\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/069ad9702fd238c2762726c3ecd75aa3.webm?t=1725013500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/069ad9702fd238c2762726c3ecd75aa3.mp4?t=1725013500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>DLC - The Game是Drone Champions League官方推出的电子游戏 - 世界领先的专业无人机比赛冠军团队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/2bea83731b723cd13ba7d6bdcb7a1b0a.poster.avif?t=1725013500\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/2bea83731b723cd13ba7d6bdcb7a1b0a.webm?t=1725013500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/2bea83731b723cd13ba7d6bdcb7a1b0a.mp4?t=1725013500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有机会参与入Drone Champions League（DCL）等现实生活中举办的无人机比赛活动<br></li><li>能够与来自全世界多达30名飞行员同时线上游玩<br></li><li>适合喜欢以第一人称视角为主的人。适合即兴飞行员。适合相机无人机操作员。适合无人机比赛飞行员。<br></li><li>线上支持额外的27首音轨<br></li><li>通过3个设置实现高度逼真的飞行物理学 - 保持竞争平衡<br></li><li>获取以及解锁超过60款无人机皮肤和路线</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964570/extras/60760e017f9d5539c30e3a0f69283068.poster.avif?t=1725013500\" width